Data is gathered from the following locations:

List of countries:
http://api.worldbank.org/countries/?per_page=500


List of indicators:

Total population: SP.POP.TOTL
http://api.worldbank.org/countries/all/indicators/SP.POP.TOTL?date=2015:2015&per_page=500

GDP per capita: NY.GDP.PCAP.CD
http://api.worldbank.org/countries/all/indicators/NY.GDP.PCAP.CD?date=2015:2015&per_page=500

Life Expectancy: SP.DYN.LE00.IN
http://api.worldbank.org/countries/all/indicators/SP.DYN.LE00.IN?date=2015:2015&per_page=500

